graph TB
    Client["👤 CLIENT LAYER<br/>🌐 Web Browser<br/>HTML/CSS/JavaScript<br/>User interface"]

    CDN["🔄 CDN & CACHE<br/>⚡ Content Delivery<br/>Static assets<br/>Images, CSS, JS<br/>Fast delivery"]

    WebServer["🖥️ WEB SERVER LAYER<br/>🔧 Application Server<br/>Node.js/Python/PHP/Java<br/>Request routing<br/>Business logic<br/>API endpoints"]

    Redis["💾 IN-MEMORY CACHE<br/>⚡ Redis/Memcached<br/>Session data<br/>Frequent queries<br/>Fast access"]

    Database["💾 DATABASE LAYER<br/>📊 Data Storage<br/>PostgreSQL/MongoDB<br/>User accounts<br/>Persistent data<br/>Transactions"]

    Storage["📁 FILE STORAGE<br/>☁️ S3/Cloud Storage<br/>User uploads<br/>Media files<br/>Documents"]

    Monitoring["🔔 MONITORING<br/>📈 Performance<br/>Error tracking<br/>Analytics"]

    Client -->|"1. HTTPS Request"| CDN
    Client -->|"2. HTTPS Request"| WebServer
